Package: highlighter
Title: Code Syntax Highlighting using the Prism.js Library
Version: 0.0.1.0000
Authors@R: 
    person("Federico", "Rivadeneira", , "federivadeneira@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7818-1225"))
Description: This package leverages the power of the Prism javascript library to enhance your R Markdown (rmd) documents and Shiny applications with Code Syntax Highlighting. Whether you're documenting your data analysis or creating interactive Shiny apps, this package ensures that your code snippets are presented in a clear and visually appealing manner.
